t.net%2F2019%2F8%2F1565586308_os-1280w.jpg&h=0815daa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立即做嘢!!!</span></span></strong></div><br />\n1) 國際文宣<br />\n2) 本土文宣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">馬上非人化</span></strong></span>番港共高官及警犬，叫佢地狗係唔夠，要叫佢哋<span style=\"color: red;\">寄生蟲/老鼠</span><br />\n我唔想大屠殺開始時香港人仲婦人之仁，做綿羊等死<br />\n我敢講，好多和理非雖然唔會同勇武割蓆，但佢地太善良，都唔會忍心自己郁手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得冇感覺<br />\n但冇感覺正正就係個問題<br />\n長期洗腦，個社會就會潛意識覺得死咗都冇乜感覺，或者抵死<br />\n<br />\n打到隻曱甴爆江冇感覺<br />\n用毒氣噴隻曱甴冇感覺<br />\n射盲隻曱甴冇感覺<br />\n殺死隻曱甴冇感覺<br />\n大屠殺二百萬隻曱甴冇感覺"},{"pid":"49e59606c5df0208875eeb7b93761b552ef4f017","tid":1461560,"uid":190579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"普選時間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />寄生蟲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老鼠"},{"pid":"423bd59625ced292247de2bcf270015ad2a62c50","tid":1461560,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:20:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ede928f98c55d8581ecb7cc734b396f41d0d4338","tid":1461560,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:21:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00a53aedd056745ba14df9e1453889d1dd067286","tid":1461560,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:24:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b974e5bb635e1fccf54490a0dcddaffc865942b","tid":1461560,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:25:04.000Z","msg":"[認真討論]<br />\n我唔認同要非人化返佢哋<br />\n咁樣無形中認同咗哩種做法 <br />\n= 話畀人聽 戰爭雙方用哩種方法互相攻訐<br />\n其實由港豬、蝗蟲已經種下咗因<br />\n我覺得要正確描述佢哋 而唔係再用<strong>比喻</strong><br />\n佢哋係 民族叛徒、賣國者、施虐狂/虐待狂、psychopath&hellip;&hellip; etc."},{"pid":"b221051f381f14c6199f35e983e8428e3e53cffa","tid":1461560,"uid":27